Subject: Want to exclude domain admin group from "file share access" review
Description:
Hello,
We are testing the netwrix resource audit section of netwrix auditor.  We identified the groups for read and modify however the file share is pulling in our domain admin group for review.  Is there a way we can exclude a group like "domain admins" from a resource audit?  We don't want data owners to see the service accounts in the review.
DevOps_Steps_to_Reproduce__c: customer wanted the domain admins not to be included on the activity reports they are having
What_We_Know__c: 1. customer is doing a search activity records about the changes file file share
Next_Steps__c: see the feedback from customer and setup a meeting if needed
Solution_Comment__c:
Symptom
The customer would like reource owners to only see specific groups and users in resource review, and hide others.


Resolution
This is not possible as owners, own the resource and have full visibility into them.
